---
title: Leek Crusted Chicken with Roasted Potatoes and Carrots
description: This delicious Leek Crusted Chicken has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gsc-leek-crusted-chicken-878ed757-f7f99ff1.jpg
